title: Im sad
body: I'm sad I did not get my icon and its supposed to be at the max 20th I didn't even receive nothing to tell me I just got the skin while I went to check why I did not receive anything and I had it I hope I get a mystery skin for this ;) just j=kidding I want my icon though

replies.body: As long as you played a matchmade game by the 19th, you'll be okay and will receive the goodies in the next pass.  Bookmark the [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-) to stay up to date on our progress.  There are a lot of accounts to gift, so hang tight until this is all wrapped up!
